-   <span data-ttu-id="60a60-408">en GB です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="60a60-408">en-GB.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="60a60-409">英語 (英国)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="60a60-409">English (United Kingdom)</span></span>  
  
